    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Drishti Eye Care. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Radiologist to strengthen our Gwalior-based team.\n\nAbout Drishti Eye Care:\nDrishti Eye Care is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Drishti Eye Care!",
